Kru: "Umi? Your pace has slowed down... Are you really okay?"
Umi: "Eh? Ah... haa haa... yeah... I'm fine..."
Banka: "Do you feel unwell somewhere? You seemed fine though..."
Kru: "Yeah... You were twitching a bit... and you're sweating too..."
Umi: "I-I'm fine... so... let's hurry... and go"

Banka: "If Umi-san says she's fine, then let's get going. I'll keep an eye
from behind."
Kru: "Umi! Look at that! That bird!"
Umi: "Eh! Ah!... I'm fine! Really, really! I can walk properly!"
Kru: "No... I was just pointing out a beautiful bird..."
Umi: "Eh? Ah... haa haa... yeah... it's beautiful..."

Banka: "Man... it's true that you encounter various creatures when you
travel to unknown lands!"
Umi: "Yeah! I want to see lots of different things!"
Umi: "Then let's hurry on... haa haa"
Kru: "Yeah... with all that sweat, no wonder... Are you hot?"

Umi: "Eh? Ah... uh... yeah... it's hot... haa haa... maybe because it's
been a while since our last journey..."

Kru: "That's true... My legs are starting to feel tired too... Let's take a
break soon after we've gone a bit further."
Banka: "That sounds good. Umi-san seems quite tired as well..."
Umi: "Haa haa... that's not... the case..."

Kru: "But you've been panting for a while now... You shouldn't push
yourself too hard."
Umi: "Mmm! Haa haa... it's nothing... let's hurry!"
Kru: "Right... let's head to a place where we can rest soon."
Banka: "Yes, I think it would be easier if we get there quickly..."
Umi: "Then let's hurry on... haa haa"
Kru: "I've been calling you for a while now..."
Umi: "Th-that's... right... I'm s-sorry, I didn't notice..."

Kru: "No, that's okay, but... you're sweating a lot... and... why are you
writhing like that...?"

Banka: "Kru-san... you shouldn't say that to a girl. Girls have those needs
too..."

Kru: "Ah, I see... sorry, I didn't realize... we need to find a place where
you can relieve yourself..."

Umi: "Haa haa... th-that's... right... maybe I drank too much water
earlier..."

Banka: "Indeed, traveling as a girl can be tough. You can't go when you
need to."
Umi: "No!... I don't want to... no..."

Banka: "Ah, no good, Kru-san! If you stimulate her too much, she might
leak..."
Umi: "Uhhn... it's o-okay... it's c-calm now..."
Kru: "Really? That's good... but we need to hurry."
Banka: "Indeed... my, my... girls have it tough!"

Banka: "Is there something wrong? As expected of Kru-san! You're so
observant!"
Kru: "If you're feeling unwell, you have to tell me."
